\b Service delivery challenge
\b0 \
The knowledge of load shedding fill most South Africans with anger and fear. Since we have become so used to living in civilization. The purpose of this product is to bridge the information gap, so that the consumer can know if they are currently affected by load shedding at home, while still at the office. People like to be informed.\
The secondary goal of this product is to give local government information on which areas has been effected and to hold stats for future reference. This will empower local government to a larger extend to be fair to all the consumers and provide statistics for reference.\
And since the device is not limited by electricity due to a onboard batery, data can be send to a central website for consumer notification, but also for statistical use of local government.\
