\b \cf0 Concept summary
\b0 \
Provide information from home. As a GSM device utilizing the Vodacom network as backbone the core infrastructure this device can provide information to the consumer anytime anyplace via its mobile web information and the information is available at the push of a button.\
\
The possible uses for this device are endless:\
It measure the availability of electrical power.\
It can measure current power consumption of a household\
Measure power consumption of a specific electrical product. (a fridge that use to much electricity can have faulty insulation. Savings from fixing or replacing can save some electricity. And this device will be able to be switched on and off.\
Future uses with some adaptation.\
Measure power on Geysers, street lights or robots. Switch any electical devices on or off, browse the web, smoke detector, alarm hookup. Video feed at work from home.\
The devices are in principal open source. These devices can be used by third parties with some Adrino Knowledge and electronic skills the possibilities are endless. And it will create a niche industry for the international market.\
